title: DUPLEX SIDE x SIDE IN GREAT MAPLE GROVE LOCATION
posting_body: ['Great location with easy access to highways and on bus line, minutes to Arbor Lakes shopping center and downtown Maple Grove.', 'Close to local schools and park trails.', 'Property Highlights:', 'Updated in 2020, nice 2 BR 1 BA Duplex in friendly and safe Maple Grove neighborhood.', 'New flooring in bedrooms, hall, living room, stairs and bathroom.', 'New light fixtures throughout the house, freshly painted inside.', 'All appliances included: Washer, dryer, dishwasher, range, refrigerator.', 'New Central Air Conditioner was Installed in October 2019, new Water Heater - February 2020.', 'Deck overlooks yard with trees.', 'Newer roof.', 'Oversized 1 car garage and private yard.', 'City of Maple Grove recently installed new road by the property.', 'Quiet and Safe neighborhood, perfect for someone looking to get out of apartment life but not yet wanting the hassle of owning a home!', 'Monthly Rent $1549 +', 'Tenants Pay All Utilities, Security Deposit - $1549', 'First Month Rent, Last Month Rent and Damage Deposit are due at the time of signing the Lease Agreement.', 'Some Pets are accepted with additional rent/fee', 'Dogs Must be 20 Pounds or Less when Fully Grown', 'No Puppies or Kittens Please', 'Cats Must be Declawed, and Neutered or Spayed.', 'Tenants are Responsible for Lawn Care and Snow Removal', 'MUST HAVE A POSITIVE VERIFIABLE RENTAL HISTORY', 'PLEASE INCLUDE YOUR CONTACT INFORMATION when email with questions or to schedule a showing', 'This Advertisement will be Removed as soon as Property will be Rented.', 'This property does not participate in section 8 program', 'Surrounding cities: Plymouth, Champlin, Osseo, Crystal, Brooklyn Park, Brooklyn Center, Corcoran, Minneapolis, Dayton, Coon Rapids, Medina, New Hope, Anoka.']
